flowchart TD
    Start((Start)) --> Access[Access Website]
    Access --> Select[Select 'Book Appointment']
    Select --> ChooseDetails[Select Service & Date]
    ChooseDetails --> FetchSlots[System: Fetch Available Slots]
    FetchSlots --> ShowSlots{Slots Available?}
    
    ShowSlots -- No --> NoSlots[Show 'No Slots Available']
    NoSlots --> ChooseDetails
    
    ShowSlots -- Yes --> SelectTime[Select Time Slot]
    SelectTime --> Form[Fill Personal Details<br/>(Name, Email, Phone, Health Concern)]
    Form --> Submit[Submit Booking]
    
    Submit --> Create[System: Create Appointment]
    Create --> Success[Show Success & Tracking ID]
    Success --> Email[Receive 'Booking Pending' Email]
    Email --> End((End))
